<view class="page"><view class="title">批量参保 / 停保</view><view class="subtitle">支持 CSV 和 XLSX 电子表格，提交前统一执行字段、重复和岗位校验</view><view class="card section"><label class="field"><view class="field-label">业务类型</view><picker range="{{kinds}}" value="{{kindIndex}}" bindchange="kindChange"><view class="picker">{{kinds[kindIndex]}}</view></picker></label><label class="field"><view class="field-label">投保单位</view><picker range="{{enterprises}}" range-key="name" value="{{enterpriseIndex}}" bindchange="enterpriseChange"><view class="picker">{{enterprises[enterpriseIndex].name||'请选择'}}</view></picker></label><label wx:if="{{kindIndex===0}}" class="field"><view class="field-label">已审核岗位</view><picker range="{{positions}}" range-key="name" value="{{positionIndex}}" bindchange="positionChange"><view class="picker">{{positions[positionIndex].name||'暂无可用岗位'}}</view></picker></label><button class="secondary" bindtap="template">下载标准导入模板</button><view class="list-meta" style="margin-top:12rpx">模板含「生效日期」「停保日期」列（yyyy-MM-dd，可留空）：批量参保填写生效日期会直接激活参保；批量停保填写停保日期会用该日期登记停保</view><button class="primary" style="margin-top:16rpx" bindtap="choose">选择 CSV / XLSX 文件</button></view><view class="card"><view class="row between"><text class="strong">文件校验</text><text class="tag {{fileName?'tag-success':'tag-gray'}}">{{fileName?'已选择':'未选择'}}</text></view><view class="list-meta ellipsis">{{fileName||'请从微信聊天文件或本地文件中选择'}}</view><view wx:if="{{rows.length}}" class="card-plain" style="margin-top:20rpx;background:#eff9f5">已预检 {{rows.length}} 行可用数据</view><view wx:for="{{errors}}" wx:key="row" class="card-plain" style="margin-top:14rpx;background:#fff0f2;color:#d94357">第 {{item.row}} 行：{{item.message}}</view></view><button class="primary" loading="{{loading}}" disabled="{{loading||!filePath}}" bindtap="submit">{{kindIndex===0?'提交批量参保':'提交批量停保'}}</button></view>
